;s:9:\"education\";i:4;s:8:\"learning\";i:5;s:26:\"learning management system\";i:6;s:10:\"learnpress\";i:7;s:3:\"lms\";i:8;s:13:\"online course\";i:9;s:16:\"online education\";i:10;s:15:\"online learning\";i:11;s:8:\"teaching\";i:12;s:8:\"training\";i:13;s:15:\"training center\";}s:9:\"discounts\";a:0:{}}i:20370918;a:25:{s:2:\"id\";i:20370918;s:4:\"name\";s:46:\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme\";s:11:\"description\";s:758:\"\n\n \n\n\n \n\n\n	\n\n\nThe Course Builder WordPress Theme is a high quality LMS (Learning Management System) theme for Corporate, Multisite Business, Group, Company… to create training websites for employees. The flexibility and power of Course Builder can help you easily create beautiful online courses, share your knowledge to your employees. With Course Builder WordPress Theme, you will have a perfect LMS for training website built from LearnPress – 1# LMS WordPress Plugin. \nThe Course Builder WordPress Theme with LSM made exclusively for you – Course Builder\nShare your knowledge and inspire your employees.\nImprove your employees’ skills with beautiful online courses.\nTrain your employees online with video and text lesson content, quizzes, multipl\";s:16:\"description_html\";s:8799:\"<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/course-builder-wordpress-learning-management-system-theme-elearning-software/20370918#item-description__changelogs\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-changelog.jpg\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 1\" /></a> </td>\n<td><a href=\"http://docspress.thimpress.com/course-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-docs.jpg\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 2\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/how-to-get-help-from-the-thimpress-support/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-support.jpg\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 3\" /></a></td>\n</tr> \n</table>\n\n	<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/eduma-theme.png\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 4\" /></a></p>\n\n\n<p><strong>The Course Builder WordPress Theme</strong> is a high quality LMS (Learning Management System) theme for Corporate, Multisite Business, Group, Company&#8230; to create training websites for employees. The flexibility and power of Course Builder can help you easily create beautiful online courses, share your knowledge to your employees. With <strong>Course Builder WordPress Theme</strong>, you will have a perfect LMS for training website built from <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LearnPress &#8211; 1# LMS WordPress Plugin. </a></p>\n<p><strong>The Course Builder WordPress Theme</strong> with LSM made exclusively for you &#8211; <strong>Course Builder</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Share your knowledge and inspire your employees.</li>\n<li>Improve your employees&#8217; skills with beautiful online courses.</li>\n<li>Train your employees online with video and text lesson content, quizzes, multiple question types, certificate, comment system, email notification, online webinar,&#8230;.</li>\n<li>An online corporate training website which is easy to implement, easy to use and dose not take much of your time.</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Sc_2.jpg\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 5\" />\n<a href=\"http://coursebuilder.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/highlight-coursebuilder.png\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 6\" /></a>\n\n	<p><strong>Course Builder WordPress Theme features:</strong></p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>Course Builder</strong> is a Modern Creative Multi-Niche, Multi-Purpose Training based Learning Management System which is suitable for training, teaching and coaching. If you are building an online training website with Learning Management System feature, <strong>Course Builder</strong> is definitely a great theme for you.</p>\n\n\n	<p><strong>LearnPress</strong> &#8211; <strong>LMS WordPress Plugin</strong> by <strong>ThimPress</strong> on <strong>WordPressORG</strong>.\n</p><ul>\n     <li>LMS Course Collection &#8211; combine particular courses into collections.</li>\n     <li>LMS Course Review/Rating.</li>\n     <li>Free Course, publicly accessible course support.</li>\n     <li>Lessons Management with powerful WordPress Core Editor improved to support: video, attachments in any type of media.</li>\n     <li>Quizzes Management with multiple Question Types.</li>\n     <li>Paypal, Stripe, Offline Payment Methods Integrated. Paypal payment method to allow to receive payment over Credit Cards or Paypal balance, Stripe payment method to allow to receive payment over Credit Cards, and Offline payment method is convenience to receive payment in offline ways. More is coming.</li>\n     <li>WooCommerce support as a shop solution and/or selling courses over WooCommerce.</li>\n     <li>Co-trainers &#8211; multiple trainers support for each course.</li>\n     <li>bbPress support &#8211; for private course discussion between trainers.</li>\n     <li>BuddyPress support &#8211; for communicating between trainers &#38; trainees in each course.</li>\n     <li>Trainee Profile.</li>\n     <li>Trainer Profile.</li>\n     <li>Trainee Certificate on course completion.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><strong>CHANGELOG</strong></p>\n<a href=\"https://thimpress.com/log/course-builder-changelogs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://thimpress.com/envato/changelogs.jpg\" alt=\"Course Builder LMS WordPress Theme Changelog\" />\n</a>\n  <table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://help.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img s