end and back-end, you easily follow the process of students. The performance is not similar due to depending on theme you using. Certainly, it helps you attend the progress and maybe you have some change if it is imperative.</p>\n\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"h-gradebook-add-on-for-learnpress\">Gradebook add-on for LearnPress</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --> <!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":599318,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-599318\" src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/learnpress-greade-book-add-on.jpg\" alt=\"learnpress gread book add-on\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --> <!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">If student list add-on is used by instructors, Gradebook add-on is a plugin for student. This plugin allows students follow their process. Specially, they realize what they have learnt or deadlines might be not completed.</p>\n\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">What’s more, the same as <strong>WordPress plugins</strong> of LearnPress, you will get full guidance. And to do all best featured, you can invest a little bit. However, over 10000 customers applied the plugins of LearnPress, this investment will not inaccurate.</p>\n\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>LearnPress Mobile App - React Native LMS app for iOS &amp; Android</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --> <!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":853687,\"width\":450,\"height\":249,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img class=\"wp-image-853687\" src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Eduma-Mobile-App_450x249.jpg\" alt=\"Eduma Mobile App\" width=\"450\" height=\"249\" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --> <!-- wp:paragraph -->If you alr